  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate whether providing patients with a question prompt
      list (QPL) prior to their orthopaedic surgery clinic appointment improves their perceived
      involvement in care (PICs) score compared to being given 3 questions from the AskShareKnow
      model
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
